        "title": "Buo Hnyangx Maiv Duqv Mbuonx",
        "content": "Mienh nyei ong-taix yiem Nam^ging bung, yiem koiv-hlen, deic-bung hlo, deic-nyuoqc longx. Mienh maiv maaih sic, yiem duqv baengh orn. Mv baac taux Yangh hnyangx caux Thhu hnyangx, zoux cuotv sic daaih. Buo hnyangx hlo, tin-dorngh nqoi, maiv guangc nduqv mbuonx. Gousu mienh gorngv: 'Tin-dorngh nqoi buo hnyangx maiv guangc mbuonx. Buo hnyangx maiv maaih nduqv mbuonx guangc.' Nqoi duqv buangh jiex-ndiangx douz buov. Maiv maaih nyanc maiv maaih hopv. 'Zuangx haaix nyungc maiv cuotv haaix nyungc.' Naaiv nyungc nqoi hlo, zoux bun Mienh nyei ong-taix aengx zuqc daic, aengx zuqc mietc."
