        "content": "Mienh mbuo guaax koiv, kouv haic, qlex heix haic, taux ga'ndiev. Wuov, ninh mbuo buaatc dauh ga'naaiv mbuoqc hlo, mv baac qlex heix haic, maiv hiuv duqv ninh mbuo buaatc haaix nyungc. 'Maaih dauh doc hlo bui wuov,' gouv fienx gorngv. 'Mv baac ninh mbuo laengz ndongh lo.' Naaiv dauh ga'naaiv hlo haic, yiem dingc haic, mienh hnamv daaih se ndongh lo. Ninh mbuo faan daaih 'ndongh lo' gu'nguaaic, douv douz zoux hnaangx nyanc. Douv douz, douz jorm. Mv baac maaih sic cuotv daaih."
