        "title": "Yiem Mbong Nyei Maengc",
        "content": "Buo cin hnyangx jiex daaih, Iu Mien se yiem mbong nyei mienh. Hnangv waac-beiv gorngv: 'Mienh yiem mbong gu'nguaaic buo cin hnyangx' - 'Mienh yiem go mbong buo cin hnyangx.'\n\nNaaiv nyungc yiem mbong nyei maengc ceix-paan daaih Iu Mien nyei yietc zungv. Jiex Sen Borngv gorngv ziepc nyeic fingx oix zuqc 'zoux mbong, gunv mbong' benx maengc. Nyeic ziepc juqv norm mbong yiem ziepc buo norm sengv se Iu Mien nyei daenx baav dorngx."
