        "title": "Maiv Gaengh Buangh Zingh Nyei Longx Jauv",
        "content": "Maiv gaengh buangh zuqc tian-kuv, maiv gaengh guangc koiv, maiv gaengh yiem mbong-aiv zoux nyanc ziex cin hnyangx, Iu Mienh nyei ong-taan yiem norm buangv-liouh nyei dorngx. Mbuox gouv mienh Zeuz Gueix-Zoih gorngv taux naiv norm longx nyei ziangh hoc:\n\n'Gorngv taux yiem Nanjing Koiv-Jien, guoqv-jaa se longx haic. Maaih deic-zinh henv zoux nyanc, Iu Mienh yaac a'hneiv haic.'\n\nYiem naiv norm koiv-jien deic-bueix, ziex nyeic fingx mienh yiem maiv qiemx haaix nyungc. Mbuo maiv zuqc baax mienv, maiv zuqc naapc laangh. Yiem Iu Mienh nyei hnyouv, naiv se laic guangc nyei longx dorngx."
